title: The No Jumper Show Ep. 30
description:
00:50 Camg1rl at home sick 1:00 Is beer still cool to drink? 3:15 Adam22 and Housephone reminisce about random LA adventures 5:25 Seeing the evolution of people’s drug use over the years 7:20 How do you transition from the random homie backstage to serving a purpose? 9:20 Adam22 recaps his trip to Nickerson Gardens with Killer Twan 11:00 Avoiding beef with others because of vlog footage 14:15 Housephone almost gets caught up with woman in the projects 19:27 Adam22 continues Killer Twan / Nickerson Gardens story 21:38 Housephone school Adam22 on Blue Bucks Clan 23:00 Housephone attempts to guess who Adam22 has lined up for next interview 24:20 Can Griselda Records be considered Kings of NYC from Buffalo, NY 26:50 Housephone’s barber gets left on read 30:27 How Housephone got booked at Rolling Loud? 31:35 Doja Cat tell’s Rolling Loud not to book her because their audience aren’t her fans 33:35 Housephone recalls Doja Cat deleting ex boyfriend’s hard drive with his unreleased album 36:25 Kehlani airs out relationship troubles with YG in new song 45:35 “Turning down a bad bitch will make you legendary.” - Royce the 5’9 48:08 DJ Drama gets caught cheating. Girlfriend and side chick link up. 54:38 Adam22 gives his Hawkins Burger review 55:40 TK Kirkland asked off the wall question to off camera employe 57:10 Adam22 tunes into Yuriy’s livestream with his new girlfriend 1:00:50 Remembering classic scenes from It’s Always Sunny in Philadelphia 1:01:59 Matt Ox trolls Adam22 during No Jumper Interview 1:06:44 Young Thug & Lil Boosie share their thoughts about Dwayne Wade’s transgender daughter 1:13:30 Adam22 details Tony the Cat’s one night stand with Olive the Cat. 1:17:20 New music from Lil Yachty with Chief Keef and Tadoe from Glo Gang 1:18:09 Adam22’s recaps his Valentine’s Day weekend with LTP 1:23:22 Housephone gets the plug at The Cheesecake Factory 1:27:45 How do you know you’re being trolled? 1:28:55 Lyrical Lemonade shows out for All Star Weekend in Chicago with Jordan collaboration 1:31:17 Polygamist relationships FOLLOW OUR NEW SPOTIFY PLAYLIST! https://open.spotify.com/playlist/529mn7of2HBKdLfrAMUzcK?si=rWVBWCuWSXeh0TFYb2P-dQ CHECK OUT OUR ONLINE STORE!!! http://www.nojumper.com/ SUBSCRIBE for new interviews (and more) weekly: http://bit.ly/nastymondayz Follow us on Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/nojumper iTunes: https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/no-jumper/id1001659715?mt=2 Follow us on Social Media: http://www.twitter.com/nojumper http://www.instagram.com/nojumper https://www.facebook.com/No-Jumper-198283650194402/ http://www.reddit.com/r/nojumper JOIN THE DISCORD: https://discord.gg/Q3XPfBm follow Adam22 as well: http://www.twitter.com/adam22 http://www.instagram.com/adam22 and follow adam22hoe on Snapchat
